Partial specialization of Dense class template for 1-dimension.

Dense block, as defined in standard [view.dense].

A Dense block is a modifiable, allocatable 1-dimensional block or 1,x-dimensional block, for a fixed x, that explicitly stores one value for each Index in its domain.
